description: Revised application for the northern element of the Enderby Wharf Development comprising the erection of a cruise liner terminal building, skills academy (Use Class D1), 477 residential units (increasing from 93) (Use Class C3), retail, restaurants and cafes and drinking establishments (Use Classes A1, A3 and A4), vehicular access with associated servicing facilities, car parking, landscaping, public realm (including improvements to the Thames Path), play spaces, infrastructure and associated parking
